stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Opening
    Opening --> Focused: animation ends
    Focused --> Dragging: pointer down on title
    Dragging --> Focused: pointer up
    Focused --> Resizing: pointer down on edge
    Resizing --> Focused: pointer up
    Focused --> Minimizing: click yellow dot
    Minimizing --> Minimized: genie animation
    Minimized --> Restoring: click dock icon
    Restoring --> Focused: genie reverse
    Focused --> Maximized: double-click title
    Maximized --> Focused: double-click title
    Focused --> Snapped: drag to edge
    Snapped --> Focused: drag away
    Focused --> Closing: click red dot
    Closing --> [*]: animation
